    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2403908312" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2403908312" />
    <a title="Jennie Diplock-Storer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39490748-jennie-diplock-storer"><img alt="Jennie Diplock-Storer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1446884884p2/39490748.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2403908312?book_show_action=true">Jun 06, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jennie Diplock-Storer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jennie Diplock-Storer" href="/user/show/39490748-jennie-diplock-storer">Jennie Diplock-Storer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2403908312" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1830165226804609604">This is quite a challenging book to read emotionally. Recommended to me by Caitlin, it’s a chilling work of fiction featuring the letters a grief stricken mother’s writes to her daughter’s murderer. <br/><br/>Obviously written in the first person, this is a cleverly written &amp; empathetic interpretation of a mother attempting to deal with an horrendous loss whilst supporting her son in law &amp; grandchild. <br/><br/>There are several twists &amp; turns in this book that took my breath away. A good read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

