        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2867770542" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2089369388123351127">What a great book. Not that great is the word to really use when someone is grieving their murdered duaghter. But great in the way that it is written.<br/><br/>I could barely put the book down as it was so gripping and so raw. Ruth&apos;s grief and anger is so real and so achingly savage. Such a new way to telling this story. A very emotional account of a mother&apos;s grief.</span>
  <span id="freeText2089369388123351127" style="display:none">What a great book. Not that great is the word to really use when someone is grieving their murdered duaghter. But great in the way that it is written.<br /><br />I could barely put the book down as it was so gripping and so raw. Ruth's grief and anger is so real and so achingly savage. Such a new way to telling this story. A very emotional account of a mother's grief.</span>
