<li class='cover' id='bookCover_57060445'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/57060445-i-know-you"><img alt="I Know You" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1617894881l/57060445._SX98_.jpg" />
